name: Kendall Health Dept
tweet: As we enter into flu season, KCHD would like to remind the community that there are ways to prevent influenza illness. This includes receiving an annual flu vaccination (age 6 months & older) by the end of October.  Speak with your doctor/pharmacy to receive a flu vaccine.  https://t.co/RLcWbLmcTD

name: Kendall Health Dept
tweet: How can you tell the difference between a cold and flu?  Because colds and flu share many symptoms, it can be difficult (or even impossible) to tell the difference between them based on symptoms alone. Special tests can tell if a person is sick with flu.  https://t.co/XTwMoKR4xl
